BITS Pilani

BITS Pilani is a favoured recruitment destination.Approx. 600 students apply for placements in each semester. Almost 100% of these students succeed in bagging a job. Around 200 reputed companies were hosted by the institution in 2017-2018 placement session. For more Info visit here

  • campus tour

BITS Goa

Birla Institute of Science & Technology, Goa was established in 2004. It is duly recognised by University Grants Commission (UGC) and has been accredited with A' grade by NAAC. It offers higher education in the field of Science and Technology with courses ranging in UG, PG and Doctorate level..For more Info visit here

  • campus tour

BITS Hyderabad

Birla Institute of Technology and Science, Pilani-Hyderabad campus began functioning in 2008 .The Institute offers nearly 40 courses through 12 departments that provide necessary academic and administrative support. Computer Science & Information Systems, Physics, Mathematics, Humanities and Social Science are some of the major academic departments of the Institute.For more Info visit here

  • campus tour

BITS Dubai

BITS Pilani, Dubai Campus is the international campus of Birla Institute of Technology and Science, Pilani, India and is located at the Dubai International Academic City. Set up in the year 2000, it is among the pioneer institutions in Dubai, and exclusively dedicated to offering quality engineering and technology education. .For more Info visit here

  • campus tour
